    readTime: "5 min read",
    image: "https://images.pexels.com/photos/2219024/pexels-photo-2219024.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=800"
  },
  {
    category: "Underpinning",
    title: "Is Your Basement Rental-Ready? Complete Underpinning Guide",
    description: "Transform your low basement into legal rental income. Ceiling height requirements, permits, and ROI explained...",
